    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im buying a house in austin and i'm kinda confused. why does the earnest money have to go into an escrow account instead of just going to the seller? also what happens if the inspection comes back and there's like major foundation issues? do i get that money back?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
