      "content": "gotcha. so they are basically protecting the funds until everything is officially signed and sealed. i guess i'm just a bit paranoid about the security of it all, since it's such a large amount of money being held by a third party. is there anything i should look out for to make sure the money is truly safe and being guarded properly?",
