      "content": "You're right to be cautious; trust is important when dealing with large sums of money. The best way to ensure the security of your earnest money is to thoroughly vet the escrow company. Look for companies with a solid reputation, good licensing, and clear procedures for handling funds. A reputable escrow agent will have transparent processes, like showing you exactly how and when the money is supposed to be released.",
